content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Actress Rebecca Gayheart is expecting her first child with actor husband / nude tape co-star Eric Dane, according to reports that keep on surfacing.

The couple, who married in 2004, has been in the spotlight in recent months following the Eric Dane nude tape, in which they appear to be high.

And naked.

But Gayheart and Dane now have some happier news to report, according to reports saying she’s pregnant after working with fertility specialists.

Dane has spoken about working with fertility specialists on the record, as well as how they are trying to have a baby, so maybe this isn’t far fetched.

The rumors that Gayheart is pregnant have not been confirmed, however.

Are Grey’s Anatomy star Eric Dane and his better half expecting?

A source says that Rebecca Gayheart “had some pretty bad morning sickness, but now she’s more than three months along and in great spirits.”

Eric Dane told Ellen DeGeneres earlier this year that “We’re currently working on that. It’s funny because you get the doctors involved and they call you and it’s like, ‘In eight days I’ll have to put in some work. I will be very busy.'”

Congratulations to the happy couple of the news is true.

And to Kari Ann Peniche, for getting to see both of these hotties naked at the same time! Not a lot of people can claim that feat. You go, girl!
